"title": "2215: Jesus Christ, Son of David",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "2215: jesus christ, son of david",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>A Messianic title. Jesus Christ comes as a descendant of David to fulfil God's promises in the OT of a future king who would establish the kingdom of God on earth.</p>\n<h2>OT promises of a future king from David's line</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam7:12-2Sam7:14\">2SA 7:12–7:14</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr17:11-1Chr17:13\">1CH 17:11–17:13</a> <em>These promises are known as “the Davidic covenant”</em>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa16:5\">ISA 16:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps132:11-Ps132:12\">PSA 132:11–132:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps132:17\">PSA 132:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa9:7\">ISA 9:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa11:1\">ISA 11:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer23:5\">JER 23:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer33:15\">JER 33:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek34:23-Ezek34:24\">EZK 34:23–34:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek37:24-Ezek37:25\">EZK 37:24–37:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John7:42\">JHN 7:42</a></p>\n<h2>NT statements verifying that Jesus Christ is descended from David</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt1:1\">MAT 1:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke3:23\">LUK 3:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke3:31\">LUK 3:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:3\">ROM 1:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim2:8\">2TI 2:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev22:16\">REV 22:16</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ inherits the throne of David</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:32-Luke1:33\">LUK 1:32–1:33</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:69\">LUK 1:69</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:49\">JHN 1:49</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John18:37\">JHN 18:37</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:37\">MAT 27:37</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark15:26\">MRK 15:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke23:38\">LUK 23:38</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John19:19\">JHN 19:19</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ is called ``Son of David''</h2>\n<h3>By those seeking healing</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt20:30-Matt20:31\">MAT 20:30–20:31</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:47-Mark10:48\">MRK 10:47–10:48</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:38-Luke18:39\">LUK 18:38–18:39</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:27\">MAT 9:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:22\">MAT 15:22</a></p>\n<h3>At his triumphal entry into Jerusalem</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt21:9\">MAT 21:9</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark11:10\">MRK 11:10</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt21:15\">MAT 21:15</a></p>\n<h2>Grounds for identifying Jesus Christ as the Son of David</h2>\n<h3>His human descent</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:3\">ROM 1:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt1:1\">MAT 1:1</a></p>\n<h3>His birth in Bethlehem</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic5:2\">MIC 5:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John7:42\">JHN 7:42</a></p>\n<h3>His healing ministry</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:22-Matt12:23\">MAT 12:22–12:23</a></strong> <em>One of the signs of the Messianic age was the healing of the sick (see <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa35:5-Isa35:6\">Isa 35:5–6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa42:7\">42:7</a>).</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John7:31\">JHN 7:31</a></p>\n<h3>His ultimate victory</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev5:5\">REV 5:5</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ is more than a merely human king descended from David</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:35-Mark12:37\">MRK 12:35–12:37</a></strong> <em>Jesus Christ claim is that he is not simply a human or political king, he is the Lord, the Son of God.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps110:1\">PSA 110:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John18:36\">JHN 18:36</a></p>",
